item.title: [HIVE-12780] Fix the output of the history command in Beeline
item.description:
I executed !history command in beeline. And the following results displayed.

Beeline version 2.1.0-SNAPSHOT by Apache Hive
beeline> !history
1.    0: select
1.    1: select
1.    2: select
1.    3: select

As a result, "1." is not necessary to output. I will change the output, such as the following.

Beeline version 2.1.0-SNAPSHOT by Apache Hive
beeline> !history
0: select
1: select
2: select
3: select
item.summary: Fix the output of the history command in Beeline
